These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, chinchilla, lizard
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, librarian, chef, manager
1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
2. the manager is on the left or right of the pilot##3
3. the pilot is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
5. the pilot is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Pet      | lizard  | bird | ferret  | chinchilla |
| Job   | chef | manager      | pilot | librarian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, taxi, motorbike
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, rose, marigold
1. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsmarigold##2
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Transport   | motorbike | taxi | snowmobile   | train |
| Flower           | rose      | daffodil    | poppy | marigold      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, january, october
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, grey, apricot, white
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
4. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
5. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
6. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Birthday        | march | july | january     | october |
| Color   | grey  | white   | apricot | azure    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, juice, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, accountant, dressmaker, security-guard
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
3. the person drinking cola is between the security-guard and the accountant##2
4. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the security-guard is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | juice | cola | water | hot-chocolate |
| Job   | security-guard   | dressmaker     | accountant    | lawyer       |

