.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, azalea, zinnia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, november, february, september
1. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
3. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Flower          | azalea | zinnia   | iris   | lily    |
| Birthday   | november  | september | march | february |

