.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pineapple, pumpkin, garlic
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, frog, goldfish
1. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the person eating garlic and the owner of the frog##2
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Food           | kale | pineapple | garlic | pumpkin |
| Pet   | frog        | goldfish     | mouse       | rat   |

