.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, polish, thai, mexican
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, tennis, skateboarding, handball
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the mexican##1
2. the indian is between the polish and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
5. the indian is in an even position##4
6. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish | indian  | thai  | mexican   |
| Sport           | handball  | cycling | skateboarding | tennis |

