.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, lacrosse, cycling, basketball
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bluemaster, fonseca, oliveros
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
5. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
6. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Sport   | snowboarding | cycling | basketball   | lacrosse |
| Cigar       | cain       | fonseca   | oliveros | bluemaster |

