.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, hip-hop, punk, country
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, july, october
1. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
4. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
5. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | punk       | indie   | country        |
| Birthday      | february  | october | december | july |

