.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, scientist, coach, lawyer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, july, february
1. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the coach##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the scientist##1
4. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
7. the coach is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | bartender | scientist   | coach | lawyer     |
| Birthday   | april     | august | july  | february |

