.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, snake, goldfish, bird
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, whist, go
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing go is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
4. the owner of the horse is the person playing whist##1
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
6. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Pet   | horse | goldfish        | bird        | snake |
| Game         | whist  | go | chess | scrabble |

