4. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the nigerian is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking water is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
