.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, baseball, rugby
1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | juice | mirinda | milk |
| Sport   | baseball | water-polo | swimming   | rugby  |

