.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, trance, ambient, classical
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bus, bike, scooter
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of ambient and the fan of trance##2
2. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | ambient  | classical      | trance |
| Transport     | bike    | scooter | bus | subway   |

