.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, april, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, electrician, bartender, fisherman
1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the dancer is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in may and the electrician##2
7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | may   | april  | september      | october       |
| Job   | bartender | fisherman | electrician | dancer |

