.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, soccer, golf
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, camping, rock-climbing
1. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Sport   | weightlifting     | tennis | golf | soccer |
| Hobby     | skydiving | magic-tricks    | camping    | rock-climbing |

