.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
City: prague, hannover, hamburg, san-francisco
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, rose, bellflower
1. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbellflower##5
3. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
4. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
6. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who growsazalea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| City      | hamburg     | san-francisco | prague     | hannover |
| Flower   | rose | bellflower  | amaryllis | azalea        |

