.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, collecting, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, techno, d&b, hip-hop
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the fan of punk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby        | magic-tricks     | puzzles | fishing | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | hip-hop | techno      | punk        |

 